Requirements List

Allows one user to have multiple banks tracked
Allows user login
Each user has a name
A name consists of a first and last name
Each user has a phone number
Each phone number has one user
Each user has one email
Each email has one user
Each user has one username and password
Each user can have any number of banks
Records user credentials
There are three transaction types: debit card, deposit, direct payment
Each transaction has one type
Each transaction has a date
Each transaction has a cost
Each transaction has one bank
Each transaction has one other participant
Each bank can have any number of transactions
Each user can have any number of transactions
Each transaction can only have one user
Each merchant may or may not have a location
Each merchant has a name
A merchant name does not necessarily consist of a first and last name
Each bank has an account number
Each bank has a login consisting of a username and password
